## Quality Gates

Run quality gates at these checkpoints:
```bash
# Before commits
bash scripts/gate-runner.sh pre_commit --continue-on-failure

# After WO completion
bash scripts/gate-runner.sh wo_exit --continue-on-failure

# Full audit
bash scripts/gate-runner.sh full_audit --continue-on-failure
```

## Evidence-First

Before fixing any issue:
1. Reproduce the issue
2. Capture evidence (request, response, logs)
3. Document in WO-INDEX.md
4. Then implement the fix
